README file for the Arduino wireless, internet enabled, photographic doorbell project....

work in progress...

mail.php:
PHP script runs on remote webserver and can be used to trigger an email message with custom text and timestamp

doorbell.pde:
sketch interfaces arduino (with eth shield) with an everyday wireless doorbell buzzer so when the doorbell rings, the arduino sends the trigger to the webserver


Future enhancements:
snap a photo and upload/email when doorbell is buzzed
